{"tid":485428,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【日皇退位】明仁確定於2019年4月30日退位","createTime":"2017-12-01T02:56:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-01T14:33:44.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2a3594f3edfe44593dcf827433d24ac34a58b669","tid":485428,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T02:56:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171201/large/1512096270_a67e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171201%2Flarge%2F1512096270_a67e.jpg&h=75bfaa2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本政府特別委員會確認日皇明仁的退位安排，確定於日皇明仁將於2019年4月30日退位，太子德仁則將於5月1日即位。<br />\n<br />\n今年6月，參議院一致通過《天皇退位等相關皇室典範特例法案》，讓明仁退位後，德仁可以即位，退位後明仁的稱號為「上皇」、皇后美智子的稱號為「上皇后」。<br />\n<br />\n本次退位，將是明治時代之後採用天皇終身在位制以來的首例。也是自江戶時代的光格天皇(1780年至1817年在位)以來，時隔約200年重演退位情況。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/ 日本《朝日新聞》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171201/57527108\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171201%2F57527108&d=mavyREW5k88UA4jwoGrOxQEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=2f90449e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171201%2F57527108&h=2bb67d3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171201/57527108</a>"},{"pid":"22a8d51f9c903cf929f8fa082682837ac263ba8a","tid":485428,"uid":33868,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T14:23:54.000Z","msg":"話唔定19年前已經byebye"},{"pid":"64e51d5305620798f1be446e54a8152ecd32dbac","tid":485428,"uid":24345,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T14:33:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話唔定19年前已經byebye</blockquote><br />\n83歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 起碼過多十年"}]}